Adria Manufacture is to exhibit their products at the forthcoming CIM Expo in Vancouver, Canada. The event is taking place at the Vancouver Convention Centre, British Columbia. Our expertise aims to meet the highest standards of robustness, reliability and increased safety while using the latest development technologies. Our design and constant communication with our clients have established us as a supplier of safe, durable and efficient high-quality equipment. For more information, please contact Adria Manufacture or visit company booth 1140 at CIM Expo between 6 and 9 May 2018.